ğŸ–¥ï¸ Local Setup 
1. Clone Repository
git clone https://github.com/akhilr13/monday-bi-agent.git
cd monday-bi-agent

2. Install Dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

3. Set Environment Variable

Create .env file:

MONDAY_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

4. Run App
streamlit run app.py



